title: Balsamic-Onion Pork Tenderloin with Parmesan Veggies
description: This dish will have you licking your lips in anticipation! Tender onions melt in a rich balsamic sauce that spills over juicy pork tenderloin. On the side, there's savoury Parmesan tumbled veggies that provide the perfect balance for the natural sweetness of the balsamic onions!

